Sentencas: The electrical, mechanical and thermal properties of the 8 mol% yttria-stabilized zirconia (8YSZ) and alumina composites have been examined as a function of the alumina content.
Titulo: CUBIC-STABILIZED ZIRCONIA AND ALUMINA COMPOSITES AS ELECTROLYTES IN PLANAR TYPE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The temperature dependence of bending strength of 8YSZ showed a minimum at 500-degrees-C. The strength at 1000-degrees-C was 250 MPa, almost comparable to that at room temperature (RT).
Titulo: CUBIC-STABILIZED ZIRCONIA AND ALUMINA COMPOSITES AS ELECTROLYTES IN PLANAR TYPE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The strength of the composites increased with increasing alumina content up to 20 wt%.
Titulo: CUBIC-STABILIZED ZIRCONIA AND ALUMINA COMPOSITES AS ELECTROLYTES IN PLANAR TYPE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The composite with 20 wt% Al2O3 (20A8YSZ) showed a 3-point bending strength of 320 MPa and an excellent thermal shock resistance.
Titulo: CUBIC-STABILIZED ZIRCONIA AND ALUMINA COMPOSITES AS ELECTROLYTES IN PLANAR TYPE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The thermal conductivity of the composite increased and the thermal expansion coefficient decreased with increasing alumina content.
Titulo: CUBIC-STABILIZED ZIRCONIA AND ALUMINA COMPOSITES AS ELECTROLYTES IN PLANAR TYPE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of the composites at 1000-degrees-C increased slightly with increasing Al2O3 content up to 1 wt% and decreased monotonically with alumina content.
Titulo: CUBIC-STABILIZED ZIRCONIA AND ALUMINA COMPOSITES AS ELECTROLYTES IN PLANAR TYPE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The conductivity of 20A8YSZ was 1.0 x 10(-1) S/cm at 1000-degrees-C.
Titulo: CUBIC-STABILIZED ZIRCONIA AND ALUMINA COMPOSITES AS ELECTROLYTES IN PLANAR TYPE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS
